author: joyce
msg: CLIMATE-299 - Fix test_rcmed breaking when run outside of tests
- Very hacky fix. Use inspect to get the location of the test_rcmed
module. Use this path to find the full location of the resource files
that are needed for the tests. Ultimately, the resource files need to
be moved to an agreed upon location in the project or (hopefully)
removed so the tests can be run independently.
